Name: Secret Neighbor Beta
About the game: This is an ALPHA version of Hello Neighbor Multiplayer Game, Secret Neighbor. Secret Neighbor is a Multiplayer Social Horror game set in the Hello Neighbor universe. A group of kids tries to sneak into their creepy Neighbor's basement to rescue their missing friend. The only problem is one of the players is a traitor in disguise. Playing as a child: Collect keys Save you friends from the Neighbor Cooperate but don`t trust anyone If you are lucky enough to play as Neighbor The house is your territory! Use it to separate, scare and confuse intruders. Use your gadgets to get advantage over the kids' team. Gain trust amongst your foes and attack in the right moment. Protect your basement!
